<div>
  <h3>What is budgeting?</h3>
  <p> Straight from the dictionary is the best way to explain this: "Budgeting is a quantified financial plan for a forthcoming accounting period." It involves strategic plans of spending, saving and maintaining a view on where your income is going.</p>
</div>

